Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well? Isn't it a gorgeous view?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-My heart definitely isn't racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, be tsundere all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And let's enjoy this situation\Nwhere we're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All alone, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, let us confirm our love for each other,\Nwithout any constraints!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You guys seriously haven't gone\Nto an overseas event? Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa-san, perhaps you've\Nbeen invited at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you have. You've just forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, how about we go to one,\Neven if it's domestic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll call it the\N"Summer Data Collection and Writing Camp"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you participate, you can see me\Nand Muramasa in lewd swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Why am I involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will not wear one!\NI will never wear one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Izumi-kun, you were able to come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}At first, you said you won't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, go to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. You'll get some new data, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm drawing illustrations\Nfor "The World's Cutest Younger Sister".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, Izumi-sensei, do your best to get new data\Nto write the "continuation" of that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So we can make our dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. If you say so, Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That, and I've already talked things out\Nwith Elf-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In return for lending Nii-san out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}So, is Senpai still—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I have arrived quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Senpai, those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-This is part of my contract\Nwith Eromanga-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-Is it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you're really cute. I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You big idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome to my island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To be precise,\Nthe island where my novels took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,True, somehow it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. It's not the Elven Forest,\Nbut Elf's Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a pilgrimage of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A real elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To think one really existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aniki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.\NThis is my editor and older brother, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Yamada Chris\Nof the Full-Drive Bunko editorial division.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So Elf-sensei's editor is her older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to think, we've met once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hear this is a "data collection"\Nand "writing camp".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I cannot leave it to my younger sister alone, so\NI will also reside on this island for the duration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I said that was unnecessary,\Nas you are all my frie... faithful servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:05:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well, we're here as your younger sister's friends,\Nso feel free to be a bit more frank with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Understood. If that is the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm glad that my younger sister\Nmade friends close to her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She has all sorts of issues,\Nbut please stay friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you talking—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got it. Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Geez! You too, Masamune?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Elf, your pen-name was your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm just using Aniki's last name "Yamada"\Nas part of my pen-name. It's not my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, what is your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't tell you\Nbecause that's a maiden's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you really want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My younger sister's name is E—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to think,\NI don't know everyone's real names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For my Shidou Kunimitsu, I just changed around\Nthe kanji a bit. It's basically my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you're like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What about you, Muramasa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will not tell you. It is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And people like this\Ntend to have the cutest names.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is our vacation home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone, think of this\Nas your own home, and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We have more than enough rooms,\Nso we could each have our own rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But that defeats the purpose of a camp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, how about Masamune with me,\Nand Kunimitsu with Muramasa? Sound good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How could that be good!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Be serious about this, or die. Take your pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Of course that was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be with you,\Nand Masamune with Kunimitsu, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? I'm with Izumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, Shidou-kun, is there an issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, I'm straight,\Nso I rather not be in the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you do misunderstand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei and I\Naren't in that kind of a relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, you guys can be in separate rooms.\NAnyway, let's hurry to the beach and pla—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, do some data collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there you have it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-All alone? Where's Muramasa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.47,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz354.6\pos(632.173,260.267)}Wear these \N\N\N\N<3 -Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...not going to be here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shidou-kun said he'll be down\Nafter sending a work e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So it's just you and me, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's play together until everyone gets here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Why are you so bashful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}You need to gather data to write\Nan interesting romantic comedy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}R-Right! Data collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see. So that's why you're acting\Nlike we're lovers or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not that I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First piece of data to collect!\NThe staple event at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Now, Masamune,\Nplease apply sunscreen to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop it, you exhibitionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}D-Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I wouldn't let anyone else do this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}We need to get data on a staple event,\Nso I'm reluctantly doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Okay, I get it.\NBut at least lie face-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}You're such a loser, Izumi Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}H-Here. I'm lying face-down now.\NG-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead and spread that lewd aphrodisiac\Nslime all over my beautiful, young body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She is such a...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whatever you, the lowest of all scum,\Nwould do to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,my heart will never be at your disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not what it seems, Chris-san!\NThis is just data-collecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Second data collection point!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Lovey-dovey water splashing\Nbetween two lovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}You know, that usual "Oh, so cold!\NSheesh, how dare you?" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's embarrassing, so I rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.33,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fine. We'll start with\Nthe third data collection point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"teaching a beautiful girl how to swim".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-Impossible! My perfect plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can teach me how to swim instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't swim, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are all sorts of ways\Nto enjoy an island on the south seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, let's pull ourselves together and be\Nlovey-dovey, for the sake of data collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will not allow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamada Elf, your evil plans\Nend right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, that was faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Senpai, you refused so much.\NB-But you really are wearing a lewd swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You have it wrong, Masamune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is her! She is the root of all this evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sh-She even hid the towels!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To think I would walk out in such a swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Senpai, please, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The reason why I came to this camp\Nwas because I wanted to read your stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You have a lot of shelved stories\Non your computer, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course, I have some...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to read them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The condition Muramasa gave\Nto join this camp was to read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't mind, but just the shelved ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know, I'll write something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A new piece from Izumi Masamune-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It won't be much of anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe like an after-story\Nfor the Silverwolf series.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to read!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll finish it up during the camp\Nand hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since I'm going to write it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll write you a "super-interesting piece of junk"\Nthat I'd never be able to sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, let's continue collecting data!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When we get back, let's take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We have an open-air bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,An open-air bath, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, Masamune.\NIt'll be useless if you try to peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're not careful while climbing the fence,\Nit'll just start creaking like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's fine if you climb carefully,\Nbut you can't peek, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see, this is a good bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is kind of awkward\Nbecause of what happened earlier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You seem to get along rather well\Nwith my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, um, I don't think\Nwe're on bad terms or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei, no, Izumi Masamune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How about marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sorry to interrupt you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please marry my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, your younger sister!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait... m-marry Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't say you should right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If both of you are emotionally set to do so,\Nyou can at least get engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!\NThere's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not like that at all with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not dating my younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am not. How did you come\Nto such a misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My younger sister's tweet said\N"I'm dating Izumi Masamune-sensei".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That was a really bad practical joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. Sorry to make that misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it's not your fault, Chris-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe my younger sister is a great find,\Nif I say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's a good cook, and she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And moreover, it's fun to be with her.\NI think in the future, she'll be a good wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She may look like that, but once she falls\Nfor someone, she'll devote herself fully to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She has good chemistry with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Musical instruments, foreign languages...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She has mastered anything you can call\Nhomemaking training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's our house policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you hear it like that,\Nthat's pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So let me ask you, what of my younger sister\Nare you dissatisfied with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, if I had to give a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everything you didn't mention just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really do know her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup, my younger sister has so many faults,\Nit ruins all of her good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She never keeps her deadlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She has an attitude,\Nand she spends too much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She will never be cured of that illness\Ncalled 8th Grade Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And more than anything, she is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She is dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Her dumb moments can be cute,\Nand her pathetic lines can sound really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Elf is an amazing girl\Nwho can wipe out all of her faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She is a charming woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, she is a reliable senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I think I'm here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I wasn't already in love with someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I'd have fallen in love with her\Nfive times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see, I fully understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I fully understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:35.58,DefaultLef2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(715.5,138.222)\frz271.2}Men's Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.84,DefaultLow,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270.5\pos(723.45,116.444)}Women's Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.84,DefaultLef2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(385.133,102.222)\frz271.1}Men's Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your face is all red.\NDid you soak in the bath too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shut up! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And then, we all ate food that Elf made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it tasty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll try making it for you once I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nii-san, do you have your own room?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Shidou-kun still has\Na misunderstanding about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, how is the data collection going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I felt being on an island\Nof the south seas would be something like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll talk about certain things\Nwhile you're here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gathered things like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. Then it's a good thing you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all thanks to you sending me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go to a hot springs trip\Nor something like that sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you were obviously thinking\Nof something lewd right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well... Hey, Nii-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, a lot happened on my end, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take a look at this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can this be the cover illustration?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup. I was drawing this today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazing! She's super cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you come home,\NI'll show you the completed version.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}So, please make sure to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What would you like as a souvenir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Elf-chan's socks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're holding a family meeting\Nwhen I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where're we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Fairy Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You read my debut piece, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The model for the Elven Forest\Nin the story is this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Spirits of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think,\Nstepping foot into the Elven Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amazing. Just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is where my father\Nproposed marriage to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,However, it didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mother hated insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She said, "You're the worst to propose to me\Nin a place that's full of bugs!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But they managed\Nto get married afterwards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He kept donating time and money\Nfor about five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,begging and pleading,\Nuntil she agreed to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mother was very poplar with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I can kinda see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If it would get the person I love,\Nto love me back, I would also do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Father's ways were very pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but very correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aniki told you something weird, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Something like,\N"Will you marry my younger sister?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you let me explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My father died quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before he passed away,\NFather said to Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Please raise them to be proper adults.\NPlease keep them happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the same for any family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mother replied, "Fine. Since this is the end,\NI'll grant your request this once."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And thanks to that,\NI was forced to learn a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She said, "This is all so you can be\Nhappy in the future."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aniki quickly left our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why he feels\Nlike he has a debt to pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was raised in a strict family, but it's not like\NI have a grudge against Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rather, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I really love my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, I want to choose who I marry on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One day, Mother started saying\Nshe was going to choose my fiance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been obediently listening to her until then,\Nbut I couldn't obey that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to be absolutely sure\NI will end up happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For that, I will ascertain and decide\Nfor myself who my partner will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why you left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't run away from home.\NI talked it out with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Mother, you are such an idiot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Mother, you had fun every day\Nbeing together with Father, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Weren't you happy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"That's why I will do just as Father did."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"I will catch a wonderful husband,\Nand we'll spend our lives having fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"You got a problem with that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think that's how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I get it. You brought me here\Nso you could tell me that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you. Because of that,\NI got to see something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't finish this story without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'll say this only once. So, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're a candidate to be my husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? Th-That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm in love with you or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, well, you know. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought every day would be fun\Nif I married you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought I'd become happy.\NThat's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In-In other words, I'm being p-p-p-proposed\Nfor marriage from you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not, but you are going to propose to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll consider it in a positive light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Me, propose to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That'd never happen, because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because you will fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-In the near future, you will love me the most,\Nand not anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Never mind all of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Let's head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For today, I'll let you off the hook about here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune, I'll allow you to know\Nmy True Name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Emily. When you propose to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,call me by that name.
